# Reflection

## What I Learned

Hallucinations rarely occur in isolation. A single AI response may combine fabricated statistics, invented organizations, false medical advice, unsupported quotations, and exaggerated conclusions. Performing a systematic audit helps identify each issue independently and assess the overall reliability of the response.

---

## What I'd Do Differently

In future evaluations, I would verify every cited study, organization, researcher, and numerical claim individually rather than assuming that a professional writing style indicates accuracy. I would also distinguish clearly between correlation, causation, and expert opinion.

